reviewText: I love the Rolie Polie Olive series!
My 22 month old son loves this show! Great DVD!
Happy with purchase, would buy from again!!!
My kids watched this over and over again.  They couldn't get enough of it.  They still watch it after having it for a few months

I really like this series of stories for young children. They always about the family and family adventures and relationships
between family members
